content:
i don't feel particularly confident with descriptions and lore, the gameplay terms was very nice because we have people testing out and thus we can make our own interpretations and that part is not a complete no at least

but the gameplay wording is focused on mechanics that we can test in game, 

while descriptions(and names are a part of it) need a lot more focus on meaning that we have little to no way of knowing without the help of a translator (i would go as far as to say it shouldn't be done if the one leading it isn't already a translator)
